Package: com.nextsolution.dailyledger.smsimport
Name: Daily Ledger SMS Import
Version: 1.3.0
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64e
Depends: firmware (>= 16.0), mobilesubstrate, preferenceloader
Description: RootHide SpringBoard tweak that automatically imports QAR bank SMS containing the exact configured marker, including **6760, into Daily Ledger. Includes attributed-message decoding, recovery, status, and one vibration after a successful import. Requires RootHide Bootstrap 2.0 or later and Daily Ledger 1.3.2 or later.
Maintainer: NextSolution
Author: NextSolution
Section: Tweaks
Priority: optional
